Awesome HIT! Really it was great, and the fact that you offered a bonus for longer versions of the HIT were cool. It would be nice if you could add a worker's total earnings based on the version they took to the final page, to confirm the bonus (it adds to peace of mind). Thank you!

It seems odd to pay less for the 2nd part. You pay $4 for 10 minutes of idea generation, but then only $3 for 15 minutes of it if you get accepted for the 2nd task. Not exactly going to make people motivated when they know they are now working for less than they did in the first task. If anything, it should pay more per minute of work in the 2nd task, but at the very least pay the same minute rate.
